# Logging Requirements (Ephemeral Sessions)

meta{repo, scope, last_updated}:
your-dedicated-marketer, ephemeral_session, 2026-01-29

capture[7]{field, description, required}:
session_id, Unique session identifier, Yes
start_time, Session start timestamp, Yes
end_time, Session end timestamp, Yes
agent_id, Agent name or role identifier, Yes
model_id, Model name/version if available, Yes
actions_summary, High-level summary of actions taken, Yes
commands_run, List of commands executed, Yes

changes[3]{field, description, required}:
files_touched, List of files read/edited/created, Yes
tests_run, Tests executed with outcomes, Yes
errors, Errors encountered (summarized), Yes

privacy[2]{rule, description}:
no_secrets, Do not log secrets/tokens/credentials
no_pii, Do not log personal data

format[2]{rule, description}:
append_only, Write entries as append-only records
text_safe, Use plain text with no binary payloads
